{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1aff153e5d","title":"中共中央关于报纸、电台上的打仗宣传的通知（概要）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"00664704bb","index":0,"year":1969,"month":9,"day":3,"articleId":"1aff153e5d"}],"tags":[{"id":"268718f23b","name":"新闻广播和出版","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"91736a0628","name":"中共中央通知","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bcf63898cc","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于报纸、电台上的打仗宣传的通知（概要）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1aff153e5d"},{"id":"eae47c960e","type":"paragraph","text":"这一中共中央通知，指出：“一九六九年八月二十八日中央发布命令之后，在地方报纸和广播电台上，出现了公开号召‘要准备打仗’、‘一切为了打仗’的宣传，这是不恰当的。”“望你们立即停止所属的报纸、电台关于这类口号的宣传。”","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1aff153e5d"}],"page":{"id":"4627e2cbd8","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1aff153e5d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}